            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the meatballs are browning, peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646139110517-x200.jpg",
