            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the shallot is softening, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail and chop your<strong> courgette[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p>",
      "order": 4,
