      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>courgette, pepper</strong> and <strong>orzo</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat everything in the oil</p><p>Add the <strong>beef stock</strong> with your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
