      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the orzo with the <strong>browned meatballs </strong>and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the orzo is tender and the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>one-pot lean beef meatball, tomato & pepper orzo</strong></p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo every couple of minutes to stop it from sticking!</p>",
